      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. that makes sense. it just sounds a bit scary to me. are there any specific ways that these \"liabilities\" usually show up in real life for someone like me? like, what would be an example of something that would trigger this clause? i'm just trying to figure out how much risk i'm actually taking on.",
